#~ "you delete a task set, <guilabel>Display </guilabel>, which configures "
#~ "the fields shown in the main window and <guilabel>Storage</guilabel>, "
#~ "which configures the location of the save file, whether auto saving is "
#~ "enabled and the auto save interval."
#~ msgstr ""
